name: Robert Kennedy
summary: The news articles revolve around the potential impact of Robert F. Kennedy Jr.'s (RFK Jr.) involvement in a second Trump administration on public health policy. Despite Trump's denial, RFK Jr. claims he has been promised control over public health agencies. This has raised concerns among health experts and advocates as RFK Jr. has repeatedly spread misinformation and conspiracy theories about vaccines and other public health measures. RFK Jr.'s potential role in shaping health policy has been met with skepticism and criticism, with many expressing fears that he would undermine scientific consensus and erode public trust in vaccines and other vital public health protections. These concerns have been echoed by several members of the Kennedy family, including Ted Kennedy Jr., who has expressed alarm at Trump's disregard for public health and his decision to consult with RFK Jr. on health matters.
